%h1 Password reset
%p To reset your password click the link below:
- if @site == 1
  = link_to "Reset password", "https://agegrant.apprenticeshipsnorfolk.org/password_resets/#{@user.reset_token}/edit?email=#{@user.email}"
- else
  = link_to "Reset password", "https://agegrant.apprenticeshipscambridgeshire.org/password_resets/#{@user.reset_token}/edit?email=#{@user.email}"
%p This link will expire in two hours.
%p If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this email and your password will stay as it is.

